# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CBT Frontend — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Leave UNSET for local development — Vite's dev server proxies
# /api requests to http://localhost:5000 automatically (see vite.config.ts).

# For production (Render Static Site), set this to your deployed
# backend URL WITHOUT a trailing slash, e.g.:
# VITE_API_URL=https://cbt-backend-xxxx.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=
